translate portuguese adrians4_3765e719:

    # gg "Aw man. Is it lame if I answer that with shit I've done in a video game?"
    gg "Ah, meu. É patético se eu responder com coisas que fiz num videojogo?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:17
translate portuguese adrians4_703b8fec:

    # gg "I can't think of anything I'm really proud of."
    gg "Não consigo pensar em nada de que me orgulhe realmente."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:18
translate portuguese adrians4_de467ac5:

    # gg "I feel like I haven't done anything in my real life that's even worth talking about."
    gg "Sinto que não fiz nada na minha vida real que valha a pena mencionar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:19
translate portuguese adrians4_273854e5:

    # gg "I feel like a failure in a lot of ways."
    gg "Sinto-me um fracasso em muitos aspetos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:20
translate portuguese adrians4_7ddc1745:

    # pc "You're not a failure Adrian. You're young. We both are."
    pc "Não és um fracasso, Adrian. És jovem. Nós os dois somos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:21
translate portuguese adrians4_d93713b5:

    # pc "I haven't done anything major to talk about either. Barely pass classes in a prestigious Brazilian college?"
    pc "Também não fiz nada de especial para contar. Passar por pouco nas disciplinas numa prestigiada faculdade brasileira?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:22
translate portuguese adrians4_fdd5dffc:

    # pc "I'd say video game accomplishments count."
    pc "Eu diria que as conquistas nos videojogos contam."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:24
translate portuguese adrians4_079f653e:

    # gg "Thanks, [pcname]. That actually makes me feel a little better."
    gg "Obrigado, [pcname]. Isso até me faz sentir um pouco melhor."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:25
translate portuguese adrians4_5b60421f:

    # gg "If we're counting games, I was the lead DPS in a 120-man raid in Souls of War."
    gg "Se estamos a falar de jogos, eu fui o principal DPS numa raid de 120 pessoas no Souls of War."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:26
translate portuguese adrians4_d8f6662a:

    # gg "We were able to take down the World Boss of Radikon in 47 minutes, which is the current record."
    gg "Conseguimos derrotar o World Boss de Radikon em 47 minutos, o que é o recorde atual."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:28
translate portuguese adrians4_731af325:

    # gg "Ugh, just saying all of that out loud sounds really lame."
    gg "Ugh, só de dizer tudo isso em voz alta parece mesmo patético."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:29
translate portuguese adrians4_f21cb6bf:

    # pc "It's not lame. It's cool. And it's something you enjoy, so there's no reason to be embarrassed by it."
    pc "Não é ridículo. É fixe. E é algo de que gostas, por isso não há motivo para teres vergonha disso."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:31
translate portuguese adrians4_94825a7a:

    # gg "You're right. What the fuck am I ashamed of?"
    gg "Tens razão. De que raio é que tenho vergonha?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:32
translate portuguese adrians4_7817079d:

    # gg "It's fucking cool and I had a blast doing it."
    gg "É super fixe e diverti-me imenso a fazê-lo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:33
translate portuguese adrians4_bc26a798:

    # gg "I'm fucking proud of it damn it, and I'm tired of hiding it."
    gg "Tenho muito orgulho nisso, raios, e estou farto de o esconder."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:34
translate portuguese adrians4_d6117d55:

    # pc "There you go. Own it. Be proud."
    pc "É isso mesmo. Assume. Sente-te orgulhoso."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians4.rpy:35
translate portuguese adrians4_ae74e4a6:

    # gg "I will. From now on, no more hiding who I am."
    gg "Vou fazê-lo. A partir de agora, não vou esconder mais quem sou."

